<informationtext name="Information">
<![CDATA[
<p>The Department of Human Ecology offers two minors: Aging &amp; Adult Development &amp; <a href="/departments-programs-degrees/human-ecology/human-development-minor/">Human Development</a>.</p>
<h2>Minor Advisor</h2>
<p>Meng Huo; see academic advisor <a href="mailto:gerdman@ucdavis.edu" target="_blank">Galyna Erdman</a> in 1331 Hart Hall.</p>
]]>
</informationtext>
